data.description: Charming family home that needs a new family to love!  This 3 BR, 1 1/2 BA has newer vinyl windows and almost new vinyl patio door.  Patio has a new ceiling and overlooks a large back yard with a privacy fence.  Let's go look today!!  Sellers are offering $5,000 in redecorating or closing cost money!
